{"tid":798622,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩作品動畫做到比漫畫好","createTime":"2018-08-29T12:04:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T21:41:36.000Z","uid":103750,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"216591ee4ced567b0ea4b804f02db285ed02639a","tid":798622,"uid":103750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:04:05.000Z","msg":"好多時動畫都改左劇情/細節<br />\n有d節奏做到好差拖到慢曬<br />\n令到原作fans不滿<br />\n相反有邊d動畫化左而整得好睇過漫畫<br />\n銀魂一定係首選<br />\n中間加既原創仲有長篇都整到岩岩好<br />\n特別將軍暗殺同別了真選組<br />\n最後將軍訓係澄夜到死，服部殺埋自己朋友都救唔到將軍<br />\n異三朗既過去<br />\n比漫畫做得更加令人難忘同深刻<br />\n仲有冇其他例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c8472c212da254355ab934c88904bb5e2d72d60","tid":798622,"uid":28378,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:05:42.000Z","msg":"EVA"},{"pid":"f6f9309262264551f65f6c6e8015e81981c8c4dd","tid":798622,"uid":68085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:06:21.000Z","msg":"美好世界"},{"pid":"65ef4c0c0e171d439329c49ff904b1a0a17fa8f6","tid":798622,"uid":197836,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:06:51.000Z","msg":"寶石之國<br />\n漫畫完全唔知畫乜"},{"pid":"a2458f096df59272d0a24e3ff17fd673a231fd72","tid":798622,"uid":67719,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:07:23.000Z","msg":"個人覺得動作類<br />\n<br />\n例如 <br />\n<br />\n狐忍<br />\n進擊的巨人"},{"pid":"abcee95e9c3d5a65183e9fe026766fee5796186e","tid":798622,"uid":302,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:08:11.000Z","msg":"死亡筆記<br />\n鋼之鍊金術師"},{"pid":"bc2c060f90da0af9c7f7fe3aa0f7a89307a848bb","tid":798622,"uid":119330,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:10:04.000Z","msg":"機動戰艦<br />\n<br />\n電視版 真係好撚正<br />\n劇場版 更加正"},{"pid":"76ce1c5ad473a2a93d3c3607b4debdc585d729cf","tid":798622,"uid":200521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:13:48.000Z","msg":"悠哉日常大王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/